tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE products (
  product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  product_name STRING,
  stock_quantity INT,
  price DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE orders (
  order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  product_id INT,
  customer_name STRING,
  order_date DATE,
  delivery_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT NOT NULL,
    product_id INT NOT NULL,
    order_date DATE NOT NULL,
    delivery_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE order_item (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  order_id INT,
  product_id INT,
  quantity INT,
  price DECIMAL(10, 2)
);
